17... Nf4 $1 18. Rae1 h6 $1 {Very important- we were hoping to go for Re5 next.
} 19. Bxh6 $1 {The game is getting messy.} gxh6 20. Re5 Ng6 $1 21. Nf5 Qd7 22.
Nxh6+ Kg7 23. Nf5+ Kg8 {We can continue the fight with} 24. Qe3 $13 {The game
